run1.title: Morning double with Tanner
run1.description: He told me some big news this morning. I'm happy for him. There will probably be some big news for me coming up soon.

run2.title: Waterfall talk
run2.description: Tanner kept going off about why we had to get to the end of pipe. Everyone was excited for him. The legs felt alright today, just got to keep my mind on conference next week.
